title: They See Me Trollblin
description: The tiny Kotassians hire the Warriors to exterminate two humongous Trollblins that have invaded their village, but it turns out that the Trollblins are actually nice guys and the Warriors switch sides to protect them in a Kotassiam/Trollblin War!

title: Swing Set Jet Set
description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

title: UG Christmas Special
description: Santa and Uncle Grandpa must work through their personal differences order to save Christmas.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Too Short to Ride
description: Steven and Amethyst take a trip to Funland but run into trouble when their friend is too short to ride the rollercoasters.

title: Random Acts of Memory
description: The Warriors learn that Nohyas has been using a Selective Memory Magisword to erase select interactions with Prohyas' bizarre doppelganger their entire lives, so their new mission: take back that sword!

title: Wisdom, Strength, and Charisma
description: When Enid goes to a new school, KO sets out to make sure she fits in.

title: Special Delivery
description: Enid and Rad go on a road trip to deliver a package.

title: Robo Teacher
description: When a substitute teacher fills in for Chef, Duncan thinks it's going to be the best day ever. He's wrong.

title: Escandalosos
description: Los Osos bebé se inscriben en un torneo de lucha libre mexicana.

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Ultracolosal
description: Colosal se vuelve enorme para destruir a un monstruo altísimo, pero cuando se rehúsa a volver a su tamaño normal, el reino se enfrenta a un nuevo terror… el apetito insaciable de Colosal.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Three Gems and a Baby
description: Greg tells Steven the story of his first winter with Steven.

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Secrets
description: Grandpa Max's mysterious past comes to light when Vilgax shows up on earth in search of the Omnitrix. And the family must work together to defeat him.

title: Elect to Decline
description: Noville wants to impress Vambre with a new Magisword from the Cave of Stuff, but the Cave Weirdos are in election mode and horrible smear campaigning is making Noville's simple task impossible!

title: The More You Moe, the Moe You Know
description: Moe visits the tree house with a special birthday surprise for BMO. While BMO's mission stands on the brink of disaster, Finn & Jake host a strange guest.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: La Neblina del Paramo
description: El equipo Tennyson se hace internacional en el Omni-Copter, y la primera parada incluye una caminata por las Tierras Altas de Escocia. Pero el clima no es sólo malo, sino que hay niebla, y eso puede significa solamente una cosa: iel regreso de Niebla!

title: Cambiando Objetos
description: Axel y el equipo luchan contra la Princesa SugarSalt por la posesión del martillo de Bearbarian, que le vendió uno de los suyos: iGalileo!

title: Tales from the Omnitrix
description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

title: Mao Mao's Bike Adventure
description: When Mao Mao underestimates enemy and friend alike, it almost costs him the entire kingdom.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: A Gift for Gus
description: Uncle Grandpa's present for Mr. Gus gets loose and causes trouble.

title: Ninja Contra Lava
description: Los ninja se encuentran atrapados en una pirámide y deben escapar de la lava invasora para advertir a la ciudad de NINJAGO de una nueva invasión serpentina.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Moor Fogg
description: Team Tennyson goes international in the Omni-Copter and the first stop is for a hike in the Scottish Highlands, but the weather isn't just bad, it's foggy, and that means one thing and one thing only: the return of The Fogg!

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Rack N' Ruin N' Ratchet Part 1
description: Rack'N'Ruin join Ratchet on a rescue mission to save Jetfire, who has gone down behind enemy lines.

title: For a Few Duncans More
description: While trying to photocopy his butt on Chef's fancy new copier Duncan accidentally makes an entire other Duncan. Great! This other Duncan can do all the school stuff while the real Duncan chills. But things go badly when the other Duncan decides to copy himself so he can chill too.

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Dia de Elecciones
description: Manzana se presenta como candidato a alcalde.

title: The Shell
description: Gumball inadvertently cracks open Penny's shell and discovers who she really is inside . . . While performing a school play, Gumball is so nervous about kissing Penny that he accidentally headbutts her and cracks open her shell. They discover that under Penny's shell is an emotional shape-shifting inner self. Penny's father is determined for Penny to keep it hidden but Gumball encourages her to show the world who, or what, she really is . . .

title: Pintura dolorosa
description: Leshawna inventa una pelea con globos llenos de pintura para ver quién va al parque de diversiones con ella.

title: This Man, This Man Man!
description: When Guts Man goes on a ravenous rampage across the city, Mega Man must turn to an unlikely ally, Man Man, a bumbling DIY human analog to our hero.

title: Historia Antigua
description: Mientras Aspheera busca vengarse del "Engañador Traicionero" que la traicionó, el ninja hace un sorprendente descubrimiento.

title: 'Twas the Fight Before Christmas
description: When Princess Morbucks tries to ruin Christmas for the children of the world, the Powerpuff Girls must save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik/First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous
description: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik: It's the Haavik Show! Haavik shows up unexpectedly at the practice field and proposes he and Dan play a little game. The Awesome Brawlers have never seen this man before, but they sense something is odd about him. Regardless, when Haavik strokes Dan's ego, there's no way he's backing down from this challenge./First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous: With his back against the wall, Dan tries flipping the script on Haavik by challenging him to a game of his own - a Bakugan Brawl. If Dan wins, then Haavik will have to set him, and the other Awesome Brawler's free.

title: Separacion
description: Adorabat siente que es dejada de lado y desea que Mao Mao y Colosal pasen menos tiempo juntos y más tiempo con ella. Pero cuando el deseo de Adorabat se hace realidad y destruye la amistad de Mao Mao y Colosal, solo el secreto de su pasado podrá volver a unirlos.

title: El Desnudo de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao pierde la ropa mientras intenta escalar el Rubí Puro Corazón, tiene que regresar al cuartel general antes de que amanezca.

title: Rivales Agridulces
description: Enid se ve obligada a enfrentar temas pendientes de una amistad pasada.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Deb O'Nair
description: A classy queen of etiquette makes the Utoniums question their superhero way of life.

title: No Day Like Snow Day
description: When a blizzard hits the town, Master Frown tries to ruin everyone's fun by pretending to be a magical snowman! But when he gets frozen inside, Master Frown must worry less about ruining everyone's good time and instead not turning into a Frown-sicle, while he's forced to experience the joys of the holiday season!

title: The Christmas Special
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to destroy a gift for Santa to save Christmas.

title: Lil' Mac
description: Mr. Gus' nephew terrorizes Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve.

title: Un dia nevado
description: Cuando una tormenta de nieve llega a la ciudad, Master Frown trata de arruinar la diversión de todos fingiendo ser un muñeco de nieve mágico. Pero cuando se congela por dentro, Master Frown debe preocuparse menos por arruinar la diversión de todos y más por no convertirse en un témpano malhumorado, imientras se ve obligado a experimentar la alegría de la temporada navideña!

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 2
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Merry Christmas Mordecai
description: Mordecai has to get through a Christmas party with C.J. without messing everything up.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: El Arbol Perfecto
description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

title: Christmas Parties
description: The Bears have been invited to all their friends' Christmas parties. In an effort to have time to crash Nom Nom's huge star-studded bash, the Bears first try to make quick stops at all their friends' parties throughout the night.

title: Dangerous Dealings/The Hunter Returns
description: Dangerous Dealings: The Awesome Brawler's have become aware of a growing number of adults with illegal Baku-brawling devices. But where are they all coming from? Shun decides to take things into his own hands and sets up a "sting" operation to try to draw out the person selling the devices./The Hunter Returns: Lightning has been caught and locked up by an overly aggressive dog catcher! And to make things worse, he doesn't have his collar with Baku-balls. At the compound where he's being held, he runs into an old foe.  It's up to these two enemies to team up and escape their captor.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Access Denied
description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

title: Hideous Hound
description: Prohyas pets an unsightly stray dog, and from that moment on the poor pooch appears on a variety of Warrior missions, driving Vambre and Vambre's brain insane!

title: Dweller in the Depths Part 2
description: Optimus receives a dire warning from the Primes as Chromia and Bee pursue Windblade into a waking Titan under the sea.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Rey del Castillo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max viajan al Castillo Bishopbrook para visitar a un pariente lejano de la realeza. Pero cuando Ben se encuentra con un "fantasma" en la casa embrujada, resulta ser su nuevo rival, Kevin 11, que lanza a alienígenas aún más retorcidos en su camino: iThornblade, Undertow y Materia Oscura!

title: The Saint
description: Gumball doesn't believe anyone could really be as nice as Alan and sets out to find his breaking point. Alan is so good-natured that Gumball feels compelled to make him lose his temper. Despite turning the whole school against him, destroying his relationship with Carmen and even selling his parents, Alan remains understanding and happy. Defeated, Gumball and Darwin decide to adopt Alan's positive attitude to see if they can be more like Alan.Gumball and Darwin help Anais make up an imaginary friend who turns out to be all too real. Anais throws a party but no-one shows up as she has no friends or social skills. Gumball and Darwin help Anais make up an imaginary friend who, much to all their surprise, appears in front of them. Gumball and Darwin teach Anais and her new friend how to become friends but realize he might not be so imaginary after all.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers/The Return of Sophie
description: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers: The Awesome brawlers go to see Benton Dusk to tell him about the Fusion Bakugan and ask him if he knows anything about this character: Haavik. However, the meeting takes an unexpected twist when Haavik decides to crash it./The Return of Sophie: A video has surfaced showing Toshi using an illegal Baku-Brawling device! Shun has his hands full when Sophie starts making trouble for Kazami Holdings, accusing them of illegally exploiting Bakugan.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Ancients of the Creek
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP discover an ancient fort that belonged to the first kids in the Creek.

title: Escaramuza
description: When Val's favorite Escaramuza team loses a member, he convinces Xochi to join the squad. He becomes her coach and will do anything to win the big competition.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Ninja vs. Lava
description: The ninja find themselves trapped in a pyramid and must escape encroaching lava to warn NINJAGO City of a new Serpentine invasion.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Secret Santa
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the crew all have the same popular and hard-to-find gift in mine for their Secret Santa, their nice Christmas shopping trip to the mall turns into a crazy competition.

title: Christmas in Space
description: The guys celebrate their first Christmas in space by opening presents, eating peppermint bark and telling Christmas stories. Benson wants the stories to be more Christmas-y but the guys keep adding scary elements, which only infuriate their boss.

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: Secret in a Bottle
description: Craig needs to get a secret off his chest, so he pays a visit to the Keeper of Secrets in the Creek.

title: Bird Boy Man
description: Sumo discovers an injured roadrunner, names him Hot Sauce, and nurses him back to health. The two become inseparable pals, but Sumo learns that a wild animal can't be contained.

title: A New Dawn
description: The Time War brings Ben, Rook, and George Washington together to battle an alien conqueror.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 1
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Journey to the Valley of Repugnus Part 2
description: Bee and Grimlock navigate the strange cultures of the Energon Masters and Monsterbots, uncovering a shocking secret about the two seemingly-different peoples.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: The Final Countdown
description: Rook and his little Plumbers must defend the Base from a mysterious lockdown.

title: La Banda Pizzera
description: Los Osos van a comer a la Cabaña de la Pizza de Papá Oso y terminan reemplazando la banda animatrónica del local. iSon tan exitosos que terminan saliendo de gira!

title: La Aventura de la Moto de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao subestima por igual a sus enemigos y a sus amigos, por poco le cuesta el reino entero.

title: Mortimer al rescate
description: Cuando Craig, Kelsey y JP quedan varados en agua turbia, iMortimer debe salir al rescate!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Minus Mini
description: When Mega Mini is kidnapped by Blasto Woman, Mega Man must track down his missing partner without the full use of his own systems.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ninos vergonzosos
description: Owen teme perder a su mejor amigo Noah que se va a una escuela militar.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: You're in Control
description: When Boxman deploys a new threat, KO must turn to an old enemy for help.

title: The Blossom Files
description: Blossom's skepticism is put to the test when she believes she's encountered a space alien.

title: Wynton's Reality Show/Bakugan Soccer
description: Wynton's Reality Show: Lia has had it with Wynton's pranking, but little does she know Wynton is in for a taste of his own medicine. A prank goes too far, and Wynton finds himself in a real-life nightmare with a rampaging Bakugan!/Bakugan Soccer: The Awesome Brawlers and their Bakugan decide to have a game of Bakugan Soccer! The intensity ramps up when Pepe, his teammates and a mysterious coach show up for a little fun. It will take major teamwork for the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan to defeat this rowdy bunch.

title: Teoria de Actitud Positiva
description: Manzana y Cebollín pasan un día en los zapatos de Falafel y usan su actitud positiva para demostrar que no debería estar tan malhumorado.

title: Plane Excited
description: Clarence is all excited visit his grandma when he learns that Chad has never been on a plane. Clarence makes it his mission to help Chad get through a hectic flight.

title: The Secret of Dos Santos
description: Ben and Rook join Kai Green on a perilous alien relic hunt through South America.

title: No sin mis choco-lletas
description: Noah intenta rescatar los chocolates que Owen olvidó afuera.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Los Jovenes Titanes Salvan la Navidad
description: Santa renuncia a la Navidad, y los Titanes deben intervenir para salvar la festividad.

title: Baby Caterpillar
description: Unikitty takes in a radioactive caterpillar and raises it like a baby, unaware of the havoc it will wreak as a full-grown adult.

title: Sigue Tus Suenos
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan encontrar un sueño que perseguir para que sus vidas tengan un rumbo.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Sabiduria, Fuerza y Carisma
description: Cuando Enid va a una escuela nueva, KO está decidido a asegurarse de que encaje.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: Pizza Band
description: The Bears get pizza at Papa Bear's Pizza Cave and wind up replacing the place's animatronic band. They're such a hit that they go on tour!

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: No Me Impresiona
description: Cuando un Corazoncito no se siente impresionado con las hazañas del departamento del sheriff, nuestros tres héroes intentan de todo para conquistarlo.

title: Hachiman
description: While on a super important mission to get batteries for the TV remote Lion-O meets Hachiman, a cool Samurai warrior. Now Lion-O will do anything to prove he's just as cool as Hachiman, even if it means risking his own life!

title: Tienes el control
description: Cuando Boxman crea una nueva amenaza, K.O. debe recurrir a un viejo enemigo para que lo ayude.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Halloween vs. Navidad
description: Cuando Santa Claus intenta apoderarse de Halloween, los Titanes necesitan a un par de espíritus para detenerlo.

title: Beach City Drift
description: Steven and Connie get into a high-speed car race with their biggest foe.

title: Winter Forecast
description: Steven has to get Connie home before it snows.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Speechless on the Seine
description: While in Paris, France, Ben catches Zombozo robbing the Louvre, but when Zombozo hypnotizes Ben to remain speechless, Ben must navigate a foreign land like a mime in order to stop the criminal clown and his travelling circus.

title: Serpientastrofe
description: El ataque de Serpentine en NINJAGO City se ve desde una perspectiva inesperada, completamente al estilo de un noticiero en vivo entregado por Gayle Gossip y su camarógrafo.

title: Snow Country for Old Men
description: In an attempt to win the holidays, Chef brings snowmen to life to entertain the kids. But when they turn out to be evil, Chef and the kids have to jingle some bells.

title: The News Never Sleeps!
description: Lil' Nelson takes a job as a paperboy, which is more difficult than it sounds in a city overrun by scorching Pyro Vipers and an evil Serpentine sorceress.

title: Crisis en la roca de Ancianos
description: Una tragedia azota al Arroyo cuando los Ancianos quedan atrapados bajo la Roca Anciana. Ahora Craig, Kelsey y JP deben rescatarlos.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Side Effects
description: Ben catches a cold and the symptoms wreak havoc on his alien heroes. To make matters even worse, he has to battle a creature made from cockroaches.

title: Escape from Beyond the Cosmic
description: When Clarence accidentally breaks a local arcade game Jeff has become obsessed with, Clarence puts together his own real-life version of the game at home, encouraging Jeff to act out his fantasy in levels created exclusively by Clarence.

title: Election Day
description: Apple runs for Mayor.

title: Gumbaldia
description: Finn and Jake, as ambassadors of the Candy Kingdom, travel to a powerful new city-state in a last ditch effort to stave off war.

title: Freedom Cactus
description: Clarence draws a comic for the school paper and it becomes a huge hit with the kids. When angry parents step in and censor the comic's crass humor, Clarence must stand up for his artistic vision.

title: Teen Titans Save Christmas
description: Santa calls it quits so the Titans must pitch in to save the holiday.

title: The New Nemesis
description: When Hawkodile discovers his old enemy Eagleator has a new nemesis in his life, the gang do all they can to get Hawk back on his foe's radar.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: #FantasticBeastsAndHowToMindThem
description: Diana Prince receives a care package from home, and her pet-raising skills are soon put to the test when a mysterious egg hatches into a baby griffin.

title: The Most Dangerous Game Show
description: Ben fights for his life on an alien reality show.

title: Ultraclops
description: Badgerclops gets huge to destroy a towering monster, but when he refuses to shrink down, the kingdom faces a new terror.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: A Cut Above
description: Aki and Bert accidentally damage a bonsai tree outside the Lighthouse, sending the Lights' perfectionist gardener on a slicing-and-dicing spree as Cut Man.

title: Christmas Spirit
description: Apple & Onion have to become mall Santas to get the gifts they want for Christmas.
